Introduction

Himena is a Japanese dancer and singer.

From June to September 2023, she was a contestant in HYBE and Belift Lab's survival show called R U Next?. She was sadly eliminated in the final episode after ranking 10th place.

On October 31, 2024, Himena was revealed as the third member of MYERA. She debuted with the group on January 1, 2025 with the release of their first digital single "“Lie Lie Lie Lie / Be Naked".
